name: Gomoku Let's Go
description:
Gomoku Let's Go is a classic strategy board game. The goal is to make a line of five stones in any direction.

-Stunning Zen style Gomoku set and beautiful environment
-World-class AI with 8 difficulty levels, suits for both beginners and advanced players.
-Demonstrate your skills in 50 carefully selected challenges
-Includes both standard and Renju rules
intro: Classic board game with a Zen style!
